---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";

const lastUpdated = "June 29, 2026";
const email = "admin@ar27111994.dev";
const siteUrl = "https://ar27111994.dev";
---

<Layout
  title="Privacy Policy — Ahmed Rehan"
  description="Privacy policy for AI agents, tools, and skills published by Ahmed Rehan."
>
  <!-- Minimal top-bar matching the portfolio nav -->
  <header class="top-bar" role="banner">
    <div class="wordmark" aria-label="Ahmed Rehan — ARLabs">
      <span class="wm-mono" aria-hidden="true">AR</span>
      <div class="wm-text">
        <span class="wm-name">Ahmed Rehan</span>
        <span class="wm-studio">ARLabs</span>
      </div>
    </div>
    <a href="/" class="back-nav" aria-label="Back to portfolio">
      <svg
        width="14"
        height="14"
        viewBox="0 0 24 24"
        fill="none"
        stroke="currentColor"
        stroke-width="2.5"
        stroke-linecap="round"
        stroke-linejoin="round"
        aria-hidden="true"
      >
        <polyline points="15 18 9 12 15 6"></polyline>
      </svg>
      Portfolio
    </a>
  </header>

  <main class="privacy-wrap" id="main-content">
    <div class="privacy-container">
      <header class="priv-header">
        <p class="priv-eyebrow">Legal</p>
        <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
        <p class="priv-meta">
          Last updated: <time datetime="2026-06-17">{lastUpdated}</time>
        </p>
      </header>

      <div class="priv-intro">
        <p>
          This Privacy Policy describes how Ahmed Rehan (<strong>me</strong>)
          handles information in connection with the portfolio at <a
            href={siteUrl}>{siteUrl}</a
          >, downloadable AI agents and skill packages, and cloud-assisted tools
          or services that may route requests through third-party APIs.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="priv-body">
        <section class="priv-section">
          <h2>
            <span class="priv-num">01</span> Product modes and what that means
          </h2>
          <p>
            Some products I publish are <strong
              >local-only / download mode</strong
            >
            products. Those run on your machine or inside your own agent/runtime environment
            and do not intentionally send your prompts, files, or conversations to
            my servers.
          </p>
          <p>
            Other products are <strong>cloud-assisted / API-routed</strong>
            products. In those cases, the feature may send prompts, files, structured
            inputs, or tool output to the third-party model or API providers required
            to fulfill the request.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section class="priv-section">
          <h2>
            <span class="priv-num">02</span> Information I collect directly
          </h2>
          <p>
            When you contact me directly (for example by email, GitHub issue, or
            marketplace support message), I receive the information you choose
            to send, such as your name, email address, account context, and the
            contents of your message.
          </p>
          <p>
            For local-only products, I do not directly collect usage data,
            conversation history, or files from your runtime unless you
            deliberately send them to me for support.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section class="priv-section">
          <h2>
            <span class="priv-num">03</span> Third-party APIs and model providers
          </h2>
          <p>
            Cloud-assisted products may rely on third-party infrastructure or AI
            providers. Depending on the product, that can include providers such
            as Google, Groq, OpenRouter, hosting platforms, analytics platforms,
            and other APIs named in the product documentation.
          </p>
          <p>
            Those providers process data under their own terms and privacy
            policies. If a product routes your request through one of these
            providers, your prompt, file, or tool inputs may be processed by
            that provider solely to deliver the requested feature.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section class="priv-section">
          <h2><span class="priv-num">04</span> How information is used</h2>
          <p>
            Information you voluntarily provide is used only to operate the
            requested service, respond to support requests, investigate
            incidents, improve documentation, and maintain product quality.
          </p>
          <p>
            I do not sell or rent your personal information. I do not use
            support content for advertising.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section class="priv-section">
          <h2>
            <span class="priv-num">05</span> Analytics, metadata, and logs
          </h2>
          <p>
            This portfolio website (<a href={siteUrl}>{siteUrl}</a>) uses Vercel
            Analytics for anonymous, aggregated traffic reporting. No tracking
            cookies are intentionally set by me for this site.
          </p>
          <p>
            For cloud-assisted products, I may retain limited operational
            metadata such as timestamps, route names, status codes, and
            high-level usage signals needed for reliability, abuse prevention,
            or billing. I do not intentionally retain full prompt or file
            contents unless a product explicitly says otherwise or you provide
            them to me for debugging.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section class="priv-section">
          <h2><span class="priv-num">06</span> Data retention</h2>
          <p>
            I retain support correspondence only as long as reasonably necessary
            to resolve the issue, maintain continuity, or satisfy
            legal/operational requirements. You may request deletion of personal
            information you have sent directly by emailing me.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section class="priv-section">
          <h2><span class="priv-num">07</span> Third-party platforms</h2>
          <p>
            Products may be distributed through third-party marketplaces,
            repositories, and hosting providers. Those platforms may collect
            their own transaction, download, access-log, or account information
            under their own privacy policies. I am not responsible for the
            privacy practices of third-party platforms.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section class="priv-section">
          <h2>
            <span class="priv-num">08</span> Children's privacy and policy changes
          </h2>
          <p>
            My products and services are not directed at children under 13, and
            I do not knowingly collect personal information from children.
          </p>
          <p>
            I may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. The “Last
            updated” date at the top of this page reflects the most recent
            revision.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section class="priv-section priv-contact">
          <h2><span class="priv-num">09</span> Contact</h2>
          <p>Questions about this Privacy Policy? Reach me at:</p>
          <a href={`mailto:${email}`} class="contact-link">
            <svg
              width="16"
              height="16"
              viewBox="0 0 24 24"
              fill="none"
              stroke="currentColor"
              stroke-width="2"
              stroke-linecap="round"
              stroke-linejoin="round"
              aria-hidden="true"
            >
              <rect x="2" y="4" width="20" height="16" rx="2"></rect>
              <path d="m22 7-8.97 5.7a1.94 1.94 0 0 1-2.06 0L2 7"></path>
            </svg>
            {email}
          </a>
        </section>
      </div>
    </div>
  </main>

  <footer class="priv-footer">
    <p>© {new Date().getFullYear()} Ahmed Rehan · ARLabs</p>
    <a href="/">ar27111994.dev</a>
  </footer>
</Layout>

<style>
  /* ── Layout shell — fills viewport so Layout body never bleeds through ── */
  :global(body) {
    min-height: 100vh;
  }

  /* Top bar — reuse the portfolio nav tokens */
  .top-bar {
    position: sticky;
    top: 0;
    z-index: 80;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: space-between;
    padding: 0.75rem clamp(1.25rem, 4vw, 3rem);
    background: rgba(244, 239, 231, 0.82);
    backdrop-filter: blur(12px);
    -webkit-backdrop-filter: blur(12px);
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--line);
  }

  .back-nav {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.35rem;
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--ink-soft);
    text-decoration: none;
    letter-spacing: 0.04em;
    transition: color 0.15s;
  }
  .back-nav:hover {
    color: var(--blue);
  }

  /* ── Main content ─────────────────────────────────────────────────── */
  .privacy-wrap {
    min-height: calc(100vh - 60px);
    padding: clamp(3rem, 6vw, 5rem) clamp(1.25rem, 4vw, 3rem) 4rem;
  }

  .privacy-container {
    max-width: 680px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  /* ── Header ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────── */
  .priv-header {
    margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
    padding-bottom: 2rem;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--line);
  }

  .priv-eyebrow {
    font-size: 0.7rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: 0.12em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--blue);
    margin: 0 0 0.75rem;
  }

  .priv-header h1 {
    font-size: clamp(1.75rem, 4vw, 2.5rem);
    font-weight: 800;
    color: var(--ink);
    margin: 0 0 0.5rem;
    line-height: 1.15;
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
  }

  .priv-meta {
    font-size: 0.825rem;
    color: var(--muted);
    margin: 0;
  }

  /* ── Intro block ──────────────────────────────────────────────────── */
  .priv-intro {
    background: var(--card);
    border: 1px solid var(--line);
    border-radius: var(--radius-md);
    padding: 1.25rem 1.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
  }

  .priv-intro p {
    margin: 0;
    font-size: 0.9375rem;
    line-height: 1.75;
    color: var(--ink-soft);
  }

  /* ── Sections ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────── */
  .priv-body {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0;
  }

  .priv-section {
    padding: 1.75rem 0;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--line);
  }

  .priv-section:last-child {
    border-bottom: none;
  }

  .priv-section h2 {
    display: flex;
    align-items: baseline;
    gap: 0.75rem;
    font-size: 1rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--ink);
    margin: 0 0 0.875rem;
    letter-spacing: -0.01em;
  }

  .priv-num {
    font-size: 0.65rem;
    font-weight: 800;
    letter-spacing: 0.08em;
    color: var(--blue);
    background: color-mix(in srgb, var(--blue) 10%, transparent);
    border: 1px solid color-mix(in srgb, var(--blue) 20%, transparent);
    border-radius: 4px;
    padding: 0.1em 0.4em;
    flex-shrink: 0;
    font-family: var(--font-sans);
  }

  .priv-section p {
    font-size: 0.9375rem;
    line-height: 1.75;
    color: var(--ink-soft);
    margin: 0 0 0.75rem;
  }

  .priv-section p:last-child {
    margin-bottom: 0;
  }

  .priv-section ul {
    padding-left: 1.25rem;
    margin: 0.5rem 0 0.75rem;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0.3rem;
  }

  .priv-section li {
    font-size: 0.9375rem;
    line-height: 1.7;
    color: var(--ink-soft);
  }

  /* ── Contact section ──────────────────────────────────────────────── */
  .priv-contact {
    padding-bottom: 0;
  }

  .contact-link {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.5rem;
    margin-top: 0.5rem;
    padding: 0.65rem 1.1rem;
    background: var(--card);
    border: 1px solid var(--line);
    border-radius: var(--radius-md);
    font-size: 0.875rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--ink);
    text-decoration: none;
    transition:
      border-color 0.15s,
      color 0.15s,
      background 0.15s;
  }

  .contact-link:hover {
    border-color: var(--blue);
    color: var(--blue);
    background: color-mix(in srgb, var(--blue) 5%, var(--card));
  }

  /* ── Links ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────── */
  .priv-section a {
    color: var(--blue);
    text-decoration: none;
    font-weight: 500;
  }

  .priv-section a:hover {
    text-decoration: underline;
  }

  /* ── Footer ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────── */
  .priv-footer {
    border-top: 1px solid var(--line);
    padding: 1.5rem clamp(1.25rem, 4vw, 3rem);
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: space-between;
    gap: 1rem;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }

  .priv-footer p {
    margin: 0;
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    color: var(--muted);
  }

  .priv-footer a {
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    color: var(--muted);
    text-decoration: none;
    font-weight: 500;
    transition: color 0.15s;
  }

  .priv-footer a:hover {
    color: var(--blue);
  }
</style>
